{"tid":1819040,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"各位兄弟姊妹，有濕疹問題，可試試找下面醫生","createTime":"2020-01-10T12:14:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-11T10:18:41.000Z","uid":267909,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"34515cc7a4514cf39d30774a92eb0d66f041f2dc","tid":1819040,"uid":267909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T12:14:45.000Z","msg":"我都一直忘了，好多後生手足話有這問題<br />\n醫生本來用佢既藥已有很好效果<br />\n後來再加上我公司幫佢搞既機（哈哈係送左一部機比佢）效果更快<br />\n<br />\n我問佢攞番之前之後相再upload<br />\n下面係佢卡片<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UoFKK0D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUoFKK0D.jpg&h=101e626a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qUrJ0yZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqUrJ0yZ.jpg&h=3af82431&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"703d87f8baebe485406f14965c81f6b170b402fd","tid":1819040,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T12:15:42.000Z","msg":"麻煩大家幫手推下呢個post <br />\n等更多對於工運未好了解嘅手足睇到！<br />\n<br />\n「警世」請重視工運戰線！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1818981\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1818981</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e3a110953257ee210d81d19b16cea99b79edcab1","tid":1819040,"uid":267909,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T12:17:24.000Z","msg":"到時就話係嚟睇濕疹既就得<br />\n話係我朋友 Benson 介紹<br />\n<br />\n利申：一毫都無攞，純介紹比你地試試，因我見效果好好（唔知醫生黃定藍，但能醫好）"},{"pid":"5bae15edecab656bd425b72ecc9120109453b06c","tid":1819040,"uid":267909,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T12:28:03.000Z","msg":"這個婆婆是最嚴重個案<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u9jWBcd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu9jWBcd.jpg&h=837e0644&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"014160d263f5958c7e040b8ceb5f9e9075bb8147","tid":1819040,"uid":267909,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T12:29:34.000Z","msg":"用藥後是這樣, 後面再有更好進展（但無拿照片了）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.